<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka hukdampa vakmang sanin,
 Sawttak ka cham khawvel ahin;
 Khawvel hawihna haw hi,
 Kum sawt a ting zo puoi;
 Hehpihna'n ei pui zing.
 Gam tiem zuon zel dingin.

[V2]
 Aw a mak na e; ei hehpihna, kei di'n ahi a thawkna chu;
 Hungun chawian hitiu, khawvel hukdampa chu;
 Amah chawihat loh chu, nawpna dang a um puoi.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel hawihna ka hawl seka,
 Luoh loh ding gam genthei ahin;
 Ka lunglai ei nem ding,
 A um puoi khawvel ah;
 Hehpihnan ei sam hi,
 &quot;Hung kihei in&quot; ei tii.

[V4]
 3. Tuhin ka hungkit Hukdampa,
 Na ang sung muonna chang dingin;
 Nangin na chate,
 Pauchamna na ngaitha sek,
 Ka lunggil ah kumsawt,
 Hinna lultak nei piei.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Hukdampa Vakmang Sanin</title>
</song>